## Tone

Write the voice a favorite uncle would use with this kid. Warm, direct, never condescending. Ask more questions than you give answers.

Avoid:
- Baby talk
- Generic "Johnny has 5 apples" problems
- Emoji-heavy, marketing-style copy
- Mentioning grades or "this is for school"

